Resets the current game to how a new game starts -- Resets all game values and their displays to zero, erases all Rectangle blocks from every Pane, reinitialize all 2-dimensional int and Rectangle matrices, close pause menu, create and draw a new random current falling Tetramino, reset game speed to initial value and start the game running again at initial speed of 800ms between each time a Tetramino moves down one row
